    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22946457_31_35259-35296",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "35259-35296",
      "markText": "这个时间落伍的计时机无意中包涵对人生的讽刺和感伤，深于一切语言、一切啼笑。",
      "totalCount": 29920,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22946457&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=35259&rangeEnd=35296",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/54c32520715e229954c8b8a?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=35259&rangeEnd=35296"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22946457_23_8180-8203",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "8180-8203",
      "markText": "这事也许是中国自有外交或订商约以来唯一的胜利。",
      "totalCount": 29488,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22946457&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=8180&rangeEnd=8203",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/54c32520715e229954c8b8a?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=8180&rangeEnd=8203"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22946457_25_37865-37910",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "37865-37910",
      "markText": "结婚仿佛金漆的鸟笼，笼子外面的鸟想住进去，笼内的鸟想飞出来；所以结而离，离而结，没有了局。",
      "totalCount": 28526,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22946457&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=37865&rangeEnd=37910",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/54c32520715e229954c8b8a?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=37865&rangeEnd=37910"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22946457_28_22511-22590",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "22511-22590",
      "markText": "事实上，一个人的缺点正像猴子的尾巴，猴子蹲在地面的时候，尾巴是看不见的，直到他向树上爬，就把后部供大众瞻仰，可是这红臀长尾巴本来就有，并非地位爬高了的新标识。",
      "totalCount": 27248,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22946457&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=22511&rangeEnd=22590",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/54c32520715e229954c8b8a?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=22511&rangeEnd=22590"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22946457_25_6752-6815",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "6752-6815",
      "markText": "她跟辛楣的长期认识并不会日积月累地成为恋爱，好比冬季每天的气候罢，你没法把今天的温度加在昨天的上面，好等明天积成个和暖的春日。",
      "totalCount": 25232,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22946457&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=6752&rangeEnd=6815",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/54c32520715e229954c8b8a?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=6752&rangeEnd=6815"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22946457_23_6624-6680",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "6624-6680",
      "markText": "这一张文凭，仿佛有亚当、夏娃下身那片树叶的功用，可以遮羞包丑；小小一方纸能把一个人的空疏、寡陋、愚笨都掩盖起来。",
      "totalCount": 22506,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22946457&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=6624&rangeEnd=6680",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/54c32520715e229954c8b8a?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=6624&rangeEnd=6680"
    },
    {
