      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22946457&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=10123&rangeEnd=10164",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/54c32520715e229954c8b8a?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=10123&rangeEnd=10164"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22946457_23_3292-3388",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "3292-3388",
      "markText": "有人叫她“熟食铺子”(charcuterie)，因为只有熟食店会把那许多颜色暖热的肉公开陈列；又有人叫她“真理”，因为据说“真理是赤裸裸的”。鲍小姐并未一丝不挂，所以他们修正为“局部的真理”。",
      "totalCount": 19370,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22946457&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=3292&rangeEnd=3388",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/54c32520715e229954c8b8a?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=3292&rangeEnd=3388"
    },
